ttiğini ve bunu nasıl iyileştirebileceğimizi görün. Gereksiz masrafları fark edin, tasarruf edin ve finansal hedeflerinize daha hızlı ulaşın.</p></div><figure style="order:-1" class="md:sticky md:top-48 flex justify-center md:p-8 md:!order-[unset]"><img alt="" loading="lazy" width="1242" height="1416" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="object-contain max-h-[32rem] w-auto drop-shadow-lg md:-rotate-6 max-md:!ml-0" style="color:transparent;margin-left:-12rem" srcset="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.abonesepeti.com%2Fstorage%2Fhome-verticle-slides%2FDecember2024%2Fj6d71Hnx82k15es4nm9b.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.abonesepeti.com%2Fstorage%2Fhome-verticle-slides%2FDecember2024%2Fj6d71Hnx82k15es4nm9b.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.abonesepeti.com%2Fstorage%2Fhome-verticle-slides%2FDecember2024%2Fj6d71Hnx82k15es4nm9b.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75"></figure><div style="order:2" class="p-8 rounded-2xl space-y-6 md:!order-[unset] bg-stone-100 dark:bg-stone-900 shadow-md self-center"><h3 class="text-3xl font-medium">Kolay Abonelik Yönetimi</h3><p class="text-xl">Kendinize ve aile bireylerinize ait abonelikleri tek bir ekranda takip edin. Aboneliklerinizin başlama ve bitiş tarihlerini görün.Tüm aboneliklerinizi düzenli bir panelde kolayca yönetin.</p></div><figure style="order:1" class="md:sticky md:top-48 flex justify-center md:p-8 md:!order-[unset]"><img alt="" loading="lazy" width="1242" height="1416" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="object-contain max-h-[32rem] w-auto drop-shadow-lg md:-rotate-6 max-md:!ml-0" style="color:transparent;margin-left:0rem" srcset="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.abonesepeti.com%2Fstorage%2Fhome-verticle-slides%2FDecember2024%2FAURXeM6ykSbeJPmyEWd8.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.abonesepeti.com%2Fstorage%2Fhome-verticle-slides%2FDecember2024%2FAURXeM6ykSbeJPmyEWd8.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.a